  "root_text": {
    "iti79:0.1": "Itivuttaka 79 ",
    "iti79:0.2": "Tikanipāta ",
    "iti79:0.3": "Tatiyavagga ",
    "iti79:0.4": "Parihānasutta ",
    "iti79:1.1": "Vuttañhetaṁ bhagavatā vuttamarahatāti me sutaṁ: ",
    "iti79:2.1": "“Tayome, bhikkhave, dhammā sekhassa bhikkhuno parihānāya saṁvattanti. ",
    "iti79:2.2": "Katame tayo? ",
    "iti79:2.3": "Idha, bhikkhave, sekho bhikkhu kammārāmo hoti, kammarato, kammārāmatamanuyutto; ",
    "iti79:2.4": "bhassārāmo hoti, bhassarato, bhassārāmatamanuyutto; ",
    "iti79:2.5": "niddārāmo hoti, niddārato, niddārāmatamanuyutto. ",
    "iti79:2.6": "Ime kho, bhikkhave, tayo dhammā sekhassa bhikkhuno parihānāya saṁvattanti. ",
    "iti79:3.1": "Tayome, bhikkhave, dhammā sekhassa bhikkhuno aparihānāya saṁvattanti. ",
    "iti79:3.2": "Katame tayo? ",
    "iti79:3.3": "Idha, bhikkhave, sekho bhikkhu na kammārāmo hoti, na kammarato, na kammārāmatamanuyutto; ",
    "iti79:3.4": "na bhassārāmo hoti, na bhassarato, na bhassārāmatamanuyutto; ",
    "iti79:3.5": "na niddārāmo hoti, na niddārato, na niddārāmatamanuyutto. ",
    "iti79:3.6": "Ime kho, bhikkhave, tayo dhammā sekhassa bhikkhuno aparihānāya saṁvattantī”ti. ",
    "iti79:3.7": "Etamatthaṁ bhagavā avoca. ",
    "iti79:3.8": "Tatthetaṁ iti vuccati: ",
    "iti79:4.1": "“Kammārāmo bhassārāmo, ",
    "iti79:4.2": "Niddārāmo ca uddhato; ",
    "iti79:4.3": "Abhabbo tādiso bhikkhu, ",
    "iti79:4.4": "Phuṭṭhuṁ sambodhimuttamaṁ. ",
    "iti79:5.1": "Tasmā hi appakiccassa, ",
    "iti79:5.2": "Appamiddho anuddhato; ",
    "iti79:5.3": "Bhabbo so tādiso bhikkhu, ",
    "iti79:5.4": "Phuṭṭhuṁ sambodhimuttaman”ti. ",
    "iti79:6.1": "Ayampi attho vutto bhagavatā, iti me sutanti. ",
    "iti79:6.2": "Dasamaṁ. ",
    "iti79:6.3": "Tatiyo vaggo. ",
    "iti79:7.0": "Tassuddānaṁ ",
    "iti79:7.1": "Dve diṭṭhī nissaraṇaṁ rūpaṁ, ",
    "iti79:7.2": "putto avuṭṭhikena ca; ",
    "iti79:7.3": "Sukhā ca bhiduro dhātu, ",
    "iti79:7.4": "parihānena te dasāti. "
  },
  "translation_text": {
    "iti79:0.1": "So It Was Said 79 ",
    "iti79:0.2": "The Book of the Threes ",
    "iti79:0.3": "Chapter Three ",
    "iti79:0.4": "Decline ",
    "iti79:1.1": "This was said by the Buddha, the Perfected One: that is what I heard. ",
    "iti79:2.1": "“These three things lead to the decline of a mendicant trainee. ",
    "iti79:2.2": "What three? ",
    "iti79:2.3": "It’s when a mendicant relishes work, ",
    "iti79:2.4": "talk, ",
    "iti79:2.5": "and sleep. ",
    "iti79:2.6": "These three things lead to the decline of a mendicant trainee. ",
    "iti79:3.1": "These three things don’t lead to the decline of a mendicant trainee. ",
    "iti79:3.2": "What three? ",
    "iti79:3.3": "It’s when a mendicant doesn’t relish work, ",
    "iti79:3.4": "talk, ",
    "iti79:3.5": "and sleep. ",
    "iti79:3.6": "These three things don’t lead to the decline of a mendicant trainee.” ",
    "iti79:3.7": "The Buddha spoke this matter. ",
    "iti79:3.8": "On this it is said: ",
    "iti79:4.1": "“Restless, they relish ",
    "iti79:4.2": "work, talk, and sleep. ",
    "iti79:4.3": "Such a mendicant is incapable ",
    "iti79:4.4": "of experiencing the highest awakening. ",
    "iti79:5.1": "That’s why one ought have few duties, ",
    "iti79:5.2": "being wakeful not restless. ",
    "iti79:5.3": "Such a mendicant is capable ",
    "iti79:5.4": "of experiencing the highest awakening.” ",
    "iti79:6.1": "This too is a matter that was spoken by the Blessed One: that is what I heard. "
  },
  "variant_text": {
    "iti79:2.4": "bhassārāmo → bhassarato (sabbatha) ",
    "iti79:7.3": "bhiduro → bhindanā (sabbattha) "
  },
